data.description: This stunning ranch style 3 br 2 ba new home is well designed with OPEN entertaining areas! Rocking chair front porch! Split bedroom design as well as a spacious family room with gas logs. Light and bright kitchen with SS appliances, cabinetry galore, and an adjoining dining area. Wonderful master suite with a luxury bath that includes a separate soaking tub and shower! Additional amenities include an attached double garage and a rear entertaining patio. Priced to break the rent habit.
